<span class="headers">Shawl #8: Blessed Coldain Prayer Shawl</span>
<p>
<p>
You have made it to the final shawl!  Hallelujah!  Soon you too shall be the owner of the most drooled over shoulder equipment in Norrath.  But don't count your aviaks before they've hatched...you still have much work ahead.  Last but most certainly not least among the skills you undertake is smithing.  Happily, the reward at the end make it so very worthwhile!  Enjoy the final stages of your quest!
</p>
<p>
<b>Important Note</b>: PLEASE read <a href="#warn">The Warning</a> about the bug in summoning the Dain for this quest. I don't like to shove specific spoiler information on anyone, but this aspect could not possibly be working as intended and can result in a VERY nasty and unnecessary delay.
</p>
<table>
<tr>
<td>
<img src="http://eqtraders.com/images/articles/shawl_eight.jpg" border="0" hspace="20" align="left"/>
</td>
</tr>
</table>
